Description: 'ARutools' is a collection of functions and R code for parsing 
    Autonomous Recording Unit (ARU) data and for sub-sampling recordings. 
    Extract Metadata from your recordings, select a subset of recordings for 
    interpretation, and prepare files for processing on the 'WildTrax' platform. 
    The package allows you to read and process metadata from recordings collected 
    using the 'SongMeter' and 'BarLT' types of ARUs. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
